long_description: i enjoy watching my clients "get better", save and strengthen their relationships, reduce conflict in their families and relationships, set better boundaries, and experience a more meaningful and fulfilling life. i offer counseling and psychotherapy at miami counseling and resource center. offering a blend of traditional verbal therapies and expressive arts therapies, i help individuals, couples, parents and teens, children, and families cope with life challenges and move forward with resilience and hope. this blog offers a window into the creative process of the expressive arts and psychotherapy.
